`★ Insight ─────────────────────────────────────`
- `evaluateCondition` uses a switch dispatch so each condition type is independently testable — adding a new type only adds one case, no ripple changes
- `filterAvailableBranches` uses `.every()` so ALL conditions must pass — this matches the spec's AND semantics. Branches with no conditions are always available (short-circuit before the `.every()` call)
